png", "id": "677824147318518", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/54823267_677824150651851_3688777864047447478_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xhzL26lZfGAQ7kNvgHTZJQE&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBjFHgcLpoakTHdzfhdN7_c5-koymDu6y8N3Vq6tymMLg&oe=674DAD6E"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "329704216222612", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75250460_329704219555945_6993099148500521476_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=f-sNtXT5_gIQ7kNvgEADnDo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBk0nYhU4ftveuD3nTM_IE7zUvVUfuz_W7tvM-XrMb9OA&oe=674DB753"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "627211022861814", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031653_627211026195147_859210511188470322_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cWDHzK-E8OUQ7kNvgEj-NCo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDEYBWN8nIsmup3pKbc_wW90wrvY77wkFdAb-7Fl12EnA&oe=674DB1A8"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VRLegs", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to \"VRLegs\", where the thrill of parkour meets the immersive world of virtual reality. Step into a realm where your movements are fluid, intuitive, and empowering. Our state-of-the-art locomotion system redefines how you move, jump, and traverse in the VR space, offering an unparalleled sensation of freedom.\n\nChallenge friends or team up in heart-pounding multiplayer tag matches. Navigate complex terrains, leap across buildings, and experience the exhilaration of real-time chases. As you master your environment, you'll discover new strategies, shortcuts, and moves to stay one step ahead or elude capture.\n\nWhether you're a parkour enthusiast or new to the world of VR, \"VRLegs\" promises an adrenaline-pumping experience like no other. Join the revolution, find your rhythm, and let the chase begin!", "short_description": "Unleash parkour 